Page_0: "Damn! I can't get out of this place...I can't understand how this door can be closed so fast by the wind while I barely opened it in half an hour...And those horrible sounds and steps, they are getting closer every minute, who or...what can live in such a place? Tinker used to warn me about something strange here. I should have listened to him.
Oh, my candle is almost burned out...soon I'll face the darkness. Whatever it is coming I'll be not an easy opponent..."